Ranger Help for: disarm
=======================

SYNTAX:      disarm <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     50
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to attempt to strip the weapon from an
opponent's hands during combat. A successful disarm forces the target
to drop their wielded weapon to the ground. The Ranger must have at
least one free hand to perform this maneuver. The chance of success
depends on the Ranger's strength, dexterity, and the target's weapon
skill. Larger or heavier weapons are harder to disarm.
